title: Packer Family Office CEO Sells Sydney Home for A$85 Million: AFR
description: Sydney’s biggest home sale transaction of 2025 is a mansion owned by the chief executive officer of Australian billionaire James Packer’s family office, which went for about A$85 million ($57.1 million), the Australian Financial Review reported.
